0of%20her%20legs%20was%20tied%20to%20a%20tree.%20She%20was%20screaming%20like%20an%20animal.%20I%20called%20other%20villagers%20and%20the%20local%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%2050-year-old%20was%20found%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20her%20passport%2C%20an%20Indian%20ID%20card%2C%20a%20cellphone%2C%20a%20tablet%2C%20and%2031%2C000%20rupees%20(about%20%24370)%2C%20per%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fus-woman-chained-to-tree-india-decade-ago-to-learn-yoga-9485315%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20she%20also%20had%20a%20medical%20prescription%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20appeared%20emaciated%20and%20was%20reportedly%20taken%20to%20hospital%20and%20then%20on%20to%20a%20psychiatric%20facility%20to%20recover.%20Doctors%20said%20Kayi%20seemed%20to%20be%20experiencing%20a%20mental%20health%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnnamed%20sources%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fattempted-murder-case-against-husband-of-us-woman-tied-to-tree-in-maharashtra-2574172-2024-07-31%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20after%20her%20rescue%2C%20Kayi%20provided%20police%20with%20a%20written%20statement%20in%20which%20she%20alleged%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20chained%20her%20to%20the%20tree%20and%20left%20her%20without%20food%20or%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInjection%20for%20extreme%20psychosis%20which%20caused%20a%20severely%20locked%20jaw%20and%20inability%20to%20drink%20any%20water.%20Need%20intravenous%20food.%2040%20days%20without%20food%20and%20water.%20Husband%20tied%20me%20to%20a%20tree%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20said%20I%20would%20die%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20a%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20it%20was%20unlikely%20she%20would%20have%20survived%20for%20so%20long%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESin