n%20he%20flies%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxiom%20Space%20has%20been%20contracted%20by%20NASA%20for%20the%20mission%20and%20it%20describes%20Dr%20Whitson%20as%20%26quot%3BAmerica's%20most%20experienced%20astronaut%2C%20who%20flew%20on%20three%20NASA%20long-duration%20space%20flights%20and%20Axiom%20Mission%202%20(Ax-2)%2C%20accumulating%20675%20days%20in%20space%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20American%20astronaut%20or%20woman%20astronaut%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20Captain%20Shukla%20could%20not%20be%20in%20safer%20hands%20because%2C%20according%20to%20Axiom%20Space%2C%20%26quot%3BDr%20Whitson%20has%20over%2038%20years%20of%20space%20and%20science%20experience%20with%20NASA%20and%20Axiom%20Space.%20Throughout%20her%20career%2C%20Dr%20Whitson%20has%20held%20various%20positions%2C%20including%20NASA's%20chief%20of%20the%20Astronaut%20Office%2C%20two-time%20commander%20of%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%2C%20chair%20of%20NASA's%20Astronaut%20Selection%20Board%2C%20chief%20of%20NASA's%20Operations%20Branch%2C%20and%20deputy%20division%20chief%20for%20both%20NASA's%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20the%20Astronaut%20Office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20specialist%20in%20spacewalks%20or%20extra-vehicular%20activity%2C%20Dr%20Whitson%20has%20participated%20in%2010%20spacewalks%2C%20logging%20over%2060%20hours%20in%20open%20space.%20The%20earlier%20record%20for%20the%20maximum%20spacewalks%20-%20seven%20-%20was%20held%20by%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20who%20has%20spent%2050%20hours%20and%2040%20minutes%20in%20open%20space.%20She%20is%20currently%20at%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20waiting%20for%20glitches%20on%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20to%20be%20fixed%20so%20that%20she%20can%20return%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Whitson%20has%20contributed%20to%20hundreds%20of%20experiments%20in%20biology%2C%20biotechnology%2C%20physical%20science%20and%20Earth%20science.%20Axiom%20Space%20says%20she%20grew%20up%20on%20a%20farm%20outside%20the%20town%20of%20Beaconsfield%2C%20Iowa%2C%20with%20her%20siblings%20and%20parents.%20Born%20to%20farmers%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20become%20an%20astronaut%20after%20she%20watched%20the%20first%20Moon%20landing%20on%20television%20as%20a%20child%20in%201969.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Economic%20Development%20and%20Technology%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20Poland%2C%20Dr%20Whitson%20is%20designated%20the%20mission%20commander.%20Slawosz%20Uznanski%20from%20Poland%2C%20who%20is%20a%20European%20Space%20Agency%20astronaut%2C%20will%20be%20a%20mission%20specialist%20as%20will%20Hungary's%20Tibor%20Kapu%2C%20while%20Group%20Captain%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla%20will%20be%20the%20mission%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Whitson%20and%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20may%20work%20in%20tandem%20since%20ISRO%20says%20that%2C%20during%20the%20mission%2C%20the%20Gaganyatri%20will%20undertake%20selected%20scientific%20research%20and%20technology%20demonstration%20experiments%20on%20board%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20as%20well%20as%20engage%20in%20space%20outreach%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722685560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq6o4r82_peggy-whitson_625x300_03_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpeggy-whitson-shubhanshu-shukla-axiom-mission-ax-4-mission-us-most-experienced-astronaut-will-be-commander-for-indians-spaceflight-6255014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20trained%20biochemist%20and%20America's%20most%20experienced%20astronaut%2C%2064-year-old%20Dr%20Peggy%20Annette%20Whitson%2C%20is%20the%20designated%20Commander%20of%20the%20Axiom-4%20mission%20on%20which%20Group%20Captain%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla%2C%2039%2C%20will%20fly%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22