www.businessinsider.com%2Fexpectations-first-tokyo-visit-turned-out-to-be-wrong-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETokyo%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20for%20%24125.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20driving%20tour%20lasted%20one%20hour%20and%20took%20us%20to%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpectations-first-tokyo-visit-turned-out-to-be-wrong-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emain%20attractions%20in%20Tokyo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20stressful%20at%20first%20but%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20unique%2C%20exciting%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETokyo%20is%20filled%20with%20unforgettable%20experiences%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20it's%20the%20most%20popular%20city%20in%20Japan%2C%20which%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Ftravel%2Fworld-best-tourism-countries-world-economic-forum-2024%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%3C%2Fa%3E%20named%20the%20No.%203%20best%20country%20for%20tourism%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20city%20filled%20with%20options%2C%20I've%20found%20one%20of%20the%20most%20thrilling%2C%20unique%20ways%20to%20explore%20it%20is%20with%20a%20go-kart%20tour.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20booked%20a%20one-hour%20go-kart%20tour%20through%20Monkey%20Kart%2C%20which%20offers%20several%20options%20and%20routes.%20While%20in%20costume%2C%20I%20got%20to%20drive%20a%20tiny%20vehicle%20resembling%20those%20from%20the%20Nintendo%20game%20%26quot%3BMario%20Kart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tour%20took%20my%20group%20through%20Tokyo%2C%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplaces-in-japan-virtually-vs-real-life-comparison-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EShibuya%20Crossing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Shinjuku%20Golden%20Gai%2C%20Harajuku%20Station%2C%20Tokyo%20Tower%2C%20and%20Roppongi%20District.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2