20like%20for%20the%20movie%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20didn't%20go%20to%20audition.%20I%20went%20because%20Tim%20Curry%20had%20become%20a%20friend%20of%20mine.%20I%20had%20a%20friend%20who%20was%20in%20the%20stage%20show%20in%20LA%20and%20I%20was%20out%20there%20doing%20other%20things%2C%20and%20I%20met%20him.%20And%20at%20that%20time%2C%20%3Cem%3Eeveryone%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20a%20crush%20on%20Tim%20Curry%20%E2%80%94%20men%2C%20women%2C%20animals.%20Everybody%20loved%20Tim%20Curry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20stopped%20by%20the%20place%20where%20they%20were%20holding%20the%20auditions%20to%20say%20hi.%20I%20wasn't%20thinking%20of%20auditioning.%20I%20had%20another%20project%20and%20Tim%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20why%20don't%20you%20read%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20really%20sing.%26quot%3B%20And%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20just%20read.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20until%20that%20time%2C%20they%20hadn't%20found%20a%20way%20to%20make%20Janet%20funny.%20The%20reading%20went%20well%2C%20but%20then%20they%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20can%20you%20sing%20'Happy%20Birthday%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20so%20stupid%20to%20be%20so%20afraid%20of%20singing%20or%20humming.%20It%20was%20like%20a%20phobia%20that%20I%20had.%20I%20was%20really%20afraid%2C%20and%20I%20thought%2C%20well%2C%20I'll%20get%20over%20there%2C%20and%20they'll%20give%20me%20drugs%20or%20alcohol%20or%20something%20and%20that'll%20help.%20Of%20course%2C%20they%20didn't%20do%20that.%20I%20just%20apologized%20the%20entire%20time%20we%20were%20laying%20down%20the%20tracks.%20That's%20how%20it%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20go%20over%20well%20with%20my%20agents%20at%20the%20time%20because%20I%20blew%20something%20else%20off%2C%20and%20nobody%20was%20really%20getting%20paid.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20director.%20Nobody%20in%20that%20cast%20had%20done%20a%20movie%20except%20me.%20They'd%20all%20done%20stage%20shows%20forever