D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESilver%20Ray%20has%20two%20elevator%20banks%2C%20each%20with%20three%20elevators.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENotable%20design%20details%20make%20Silver%20Ray%20feel%20like%20an%20upscale%2C%20bright%2C%20and%20open%20floating%20resort.%20It%20could%20make%20even%20the%20biggest%20cruise%20naysayer%20excited%20to%20flex%20their%20vacation-at-sea%20on%20their%20Instagram%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20guest%20elevators%20%E2%80%94%20located%20by%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20ship%2C%20half%20port%20side%2C%20and%20half%20starboard%20side%20%E2%80%94%20are%20lined%20with%20glass%20walls%2C%20giving%20guests%20a%20full%20scene%20of%20the%20ship's%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ocean%20views%20easily%20top%20that%20of%20any%20elevator%20I've%20had%20at%20a%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInstead%20of%20a%20traditional%20pool%20deck%20with%20lounge%20chairs%20flanking%20all%20sides%20of%20the%20pool%2C%20Silver%20Ray's%20is%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20ship.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22empty%20pool%20deck%20of%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6682df16c31eb990ea2fb8a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pool%20deck%20has%20280%20loungers%20and%20picturesque%20views.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESwimmers%20get%20a%20photogenic%20view%20of%20the%20vessel's%20surroundings%2C%20similar%20to%20a%20rooftop%20infinity%20pool%20at%20an%20upscale%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20music%20at%20the%20pool%20deck%20isn't%20a%20grating%20mix%20of%20top-100%20pop%20and%20country%2C%20as%20I've%20heard%20on%20other%20cruise%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20speakers%20blasted%20what%20I%20like%20to%20call%20%26quot%3Btunes%20you'd%20hear%20at%2