r%20work-life%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20will%20some%20bosses%20just%20not%20accept%20that%20hybrid%20work%20is%20here%20to%20stay%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20transition%20is%20underway%2C%20Ravin%20Jesuthasan%2C%20a%20renowned%20future-of-work%20expert%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Skills-Powered%20Organization%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20organizations%20exhibit%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20inertia%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20adapting%20to%20the%20new%20working%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20drive%20a%20lot%20more%20efficiency%20and%20productivity%2C%20there%20is%20a%20very%20natural%20tendency%20to%20default%20to%20mechanisms%20that%20afford%20you%20the%20most%20control%20and%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20true%20of%20any%20evolution%20that%20we%20as%20a%20species%20go%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHybrid%20and%20remote%20work%20is%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20more%20visible%20areas%20where%20that%20control%20can%20feel%20compromised%2C%20Jesuthasan%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20requires%20some%20radically%20different%20leadership%20muscles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20many%20organizations%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20leaders%20feel%20they%20just%20don't%20have%20the%20visibility%20to%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20changes%20in%20the%20labor%20market%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbosses-quiet-firing-staff-avoid-public-backlash-layoffs-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiving%20employers%20more%20leverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20battle%20over%20hybrid%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20gone%20from%20during%20the%20COVID%20years%2C%20when%20it%20was%20a%20real%20seller's%20market%2C%20to%20now%2C%20with%20the%20economy%20being%20where%20it%20is%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20it%20being%20a%20buyer's%20ma