onality%20on%20both%20the%20part%20of%20the%20workforce%20and%20the%20organization%2C%20Jesuthasan%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20of%20any%20scenario%20where%20flexible%20working%20was%20ever%20conveyed%20as%20a%20right%20to%20the%20workforce%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20become%20a%20new%20normal%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20a%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20when%20you're%20working%20for%20an%20organization%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20it%20working%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20a%20steward%20of%20the%20organization's%20broader%20culture.%20You're%20there%20to%20collaborate%20and%20make%20others%20better%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20cultural%20shift%20continues%2C%20what's%20most%20important%20is%20striking%20the%20right%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20heads-down%20work%2C%20employees%20should%20have%20the%20flexibility%20to%20do%20that%20in%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20own%20homes.%20But%20there%20is%20value%20in%20coming%20together%20to%20innovate%2C%20collaborate%2C%20and%20build%20true%20trust%20and%20empathy%2C%20said%20Jesuthasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20savvy%20ones%20will%20understand%20why%20it's%20important%20and%20why%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20somehow%20retained.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fravin-jesuthasan-why-companies-enforce-rto-mandates-future-of-work-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722681782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d839bc90413ab8e1d647f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fravin-jesuthasan-why-companies-enforce-rto-mandates-future-of-work-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Strict%20RTO%20mandates%20are%20causing%20tension%20between%20workers%20and%20their%20bosses.%20BI%20spok