%20I%20can't%20overcome%20it%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20friend%20Shweta%2C%20speaking%20to%20NDTV%20said%20that%20the%20aspirant%20had%20given%20three%20attempts%2C%20but%20could%20not%20clear%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20gave%203%20attempts%2C%20and%20give%20it%20her%20all%20every%20time%2C%20but%20could%20not%20clear%20the%20exam.%20The%20pressure%20was%20growing%20on%20her.%20Even%20the%20financial%20pressure%20was%20building%20as%20the%20rent%20in%20the%20area%20was%20increasing%20every%20few%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Shweta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali's%20final%20message%20was%20a%20plea%20for%20understanding%20and%20a%20criticism%20of%20the%20systemic%20issues%20plaguing%20UPSC%20aspirants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20confirmed%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20details%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20examining%20the%20conditions%20that%20led%20to%20this%20tragic%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20comes%20amidst%20broader%20concerns%20over%20the%20pressures%20faced%20by%20students%20in%20competitive%20environments.%20Her%20case%20follows%20the%20recent%20deaths%20of%20three%20students%20from%20the%20same%20area%2C%20who%20got%20stuck%20in%20a%20basement%20after%20heavy%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20have%20said%20an%20absence%20of%20a%20drainage%20system%20and%20safety%20measures%20and%20the%20use%20of%20the%20basement%20for%20commercial%20activities%20in%20violation%20of%20norms%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20three%20civil%20services%20aspirants%20at%20the%20coaching%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722681060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fca1qd5j_test-image_625x300_03_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-upsc-aspirant-suicide-weeks-before-delhi-basement-dea