3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don't%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20vision%3B%20we%20look%20at%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20tomorrow%20and%20appoint%20a%20captain%2C%20then%20change%20the%20team%20the%20next%20day.%20Because%20the%20people%20making%20these%20decisions%20don't%20even%20know%20if%20they'll%20be%20around%20tomorrow%2C%20there's%20no%20plan%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMushtaq%20signed%20off%20by%20advising%20Pakistan%20to%20refrain%20from%20chopping%20and%20changing%20their%20captains%20constantly%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20won't%20help%20them%20in%20creating%20a%20world-class%20side.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20create%20a%20leader%2C%20where%20does%20the%20philosophy%20of%20working%20together%20go%3F%20How%20will%20you%20work%20together%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20don't%20have%20any%20plan%2C%20you'll%20make%20anyone%20the%20captain.%20The%20more%20you%20keep%20chopping%20and%20changing%2C%20the%20more%20time%20you'll%20have%20to%20give%20to%20experiments.%20And%20before%20experimenting%2C%20you%20have%20to%20create%20a%20complete%20strategy%20and%20look%20at%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20that%20experiment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20imagine%20you%20remove%20Babar%20and%20Shaheen%20and%20bring%20in%20someone%20else.%20Who%20will%20evaluate%20them%3F%20Who%20will%20see%20that%20the%20captain%2C%20whoever%20it%20is%2C%20should%20be%20made%20for%20the%20next%202-3%20years%20and%20how%20they%20will%20produce%20results%20for%20Pakistan%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20there%20is%20no%20system%20here.%20A%20system%20has%20never%20been%20created%2C%20and%20there%20has%20never%20been%20any%20ambition%20to%20create%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don't%20have%20the%20ambition%20to%20say%20that%20we%20will%20groom%203-4%20captains%20over%20the%20next%205%20years%20from%20Under-19%20to%20associations%20based%20on%20their%20performances.%20Their%20performances%20should%20be%20evaluated%20not%20just%20by%20watching%20matches%20or%20results%2C%20but%20by%20talking%20to%20them%2C%20listening%20to%20them%2C%20understanding%20their%20vision%2C%20and%20looking%20at%20their%20leadership%20qualities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20following%20this%20process%2C%20you%20will%20see%20which%20leader%20emerges.%20I%20don't%20see%20any%20of%20these%20things%20here.%20If%20we%20keep%20appointing%20a%20third%2C%20fourth%2C%20and%20fifth%20captain%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20we%20will%20never%20create%20a%20top-class%20team%2C%20nor%20will%20we%20be%20recognized%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722680280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fkq6tcivo_india-pakistan-match_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fit-doesnt-matter-ex-pakistan-stars-big-message-for-bcci-on-champions-trophy-2025-6254152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20uncertainty%20on%20whether%20India%20will%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20play%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%20matches%2C%20former%20spinner%20Saqlain%20Mushtaq%20said%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20to%20him%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20visitors'%20will%20come%20to%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fit-doesnt-matter-ex-pakistan-stars-big-message-for-bcci-on-champions-trophy-2025-6254152%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fit-doesnt-matter-ex-pakistan-stars-big-message-for-bcci-on-champions-trophy-2025-6254152%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fit-doesnt-matter-ex-pakistan-stars-big-message-for-bcci-on-champions-trophy-2025-6254152%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20the%20family%20behind%20the%20L.L.%20Bean%20empire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%