C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERTO%20mandates%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20manager's%20sign-off.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20some%20workers%20may%20benefit%20from%20it%2C%20uneven%20RTO%20enforcement%20could%20tank%20the%20morale%20of%20other%20staff.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20quest%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-level-job-seekers-quit-over-return-to-office-requirement-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20around%20returning%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20new%20tactic%20has%20gained%20steam.%20It's%20called%20working%20a%20%26quot%3Bhushed%20hybrid%26quot%3B%20schedule%2C%20and%20unlike%20other%20forms%20of%20sneakily%20evading%20a%20return%20to%20the%20office%2C%20you%20actually%20want%20%E2%80%94%20no%2C%20%3Cem%3Eneed%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20your%20boss%20to%20know%20about%20this%20one%20to%20make%20it%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHushed%20hybrid%20refers%20to%20employees%20working%20from%20home%20more%20often%20than%20companywide%20policies%20would%20otherwise%20permit%20them%20to%2C%20thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-life-balance-expectations-flexible-work-boundaries-manager-boss-challenges-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20flexibility%20of%20their%20managers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20entail%20bosses%20%26quot%3Benforcing%20a%20return%20to%20office%20selectively%20among%20employees%2C%20allowing%20flexibility%20on%20certain%20days%2C%20mandating%20on%20days%20only%20when%20someone's%20presence%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%20or%20even%20misreporting%20attendance%20in%20some%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shelley%20Majors%2C%20a%20strategic%20HR%20advisor%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boardwalkhr.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoardwalk%20HR%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManagers%20may%20feel%20that%20cutting%20employees%20some%20slack%20can%20help%20with%20employee%20satisfaction%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-stay-workplace-productivity-points-to-economic-growth-jobs-loyalty2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworker%20retention%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20doing%20so%20is%20officially%20against%20company%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20research%20has%20shown%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-work-from-home-office-culture-remote-jobs-productivity-happiness-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20work%20schedules%20can%20boost%20employee%20happiness%20and%20reduce%20turnover%20without%20affecting%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Hatim%20Rahman%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20management%20and%20organizations%20at%20Northwestern%20University's%20Kellogg%20School%20of%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20an%20organization's%20standpoint%2C%20they%20may%20have%20an%20overall%20policy%2C%20but%20some%20managers%20may%20not%20enforce%20it%20as%20strictly%20as%20long%20as%20the%20results%20are%20being%20produced%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a31ebbd-a060-47b0-84f9-26742668737d%5C%22%3E'Hushed%20hybrid'%20can%20be%20a%20risk%20for%20managers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20managers%20may%20find%20themselves%20caught%20between%20a%20rock%20and%20a%20hard%20place%20as%20they%20try%20to%20juggle%20employees'%20desires%20to%20work%20remotely%20with%20firms'%20mandates%20to%20haul%20them%20back%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspecially%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-mandates-restore-ceo-power-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epower%20has%20shifted%20back%20to%20employers%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20amid%20mass%20layoffs%20and%20return-to-office%20mandates%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20may%20see%20unsanctioned%20attempts%20by%20managers%20to%20assert%20control%20in%20ways%20that%20make%20sense%20for%20them%20and%20for