iyeh%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20attack%20in%20Tehran%20blamed%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20is%20swirling%20over%20the%20crucial%20succession%20almost%2010%20months%20into%20the%20Gaza%20war%20which%20erupted%20following%20Hamas's%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar-based%20Haniyeh%2C%20elected%20Hamas's%20political%20chief%20in%202017%2C%20died%20in%20a%20pre-dawn%20strike%20on%20his%20accommodation%20while%20he%20was%20visiting%20the%20Iranian%20capital%20for%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20President%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20context%20of%20this%20succession%20--%20a%20violent%20death%20amid%20a%20months-long%20war%20in%20Gaza%20--%20may%20influence%20the%20future%20of%20Hamas%20more%20than%20the%20individual%20personality%20of%20its%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20emergence%20of%20pragmatists%20moving%20toward%20indirect%20recognition%20of%20Israel's%20right%20to%20exist%2C%20Hamas%20members%20remain%20committed%20to%20an%20uncompromising%20approach%20to%20the%20struggle%20for%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20including%20through%20armed%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20from%20the%20group%20told%20AFP%20that%20%26quot%3Brelations%20with%20Arab%20and%20Islamic%20countries%26quot%3B%20will%20also%20be%20taken%20into%20account%20in%20picking%20its%20next%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20senior%20officials%20tipped%20as%20Hamas's%20next%20potential%20political%20leader%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKhalil%20al-Hayya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalil%20al-Hayya%20is%20the%20deputy%20head%20of%20Hamas's%20political%20bureau%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20and%20said%20to%20be%20well%20acquainted%20with%20the%20group's%20leader%20in%20the%20territory%20Yahya%20Sinwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%20Hayya%20headed%20Hamas's%20parliamentary%20bloc%2C%20which%20had%20just%20won%20elections.%20The%20subsequent%20months%20of%20political%20and%20administrative%20discord%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20schism%20between%20the%20Islamist%20movement%20and%20Fatah%2C%20the%20party%20of%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmud%20Abbas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHayya%2C%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20armed%20struggle%2C%20lost%20several%20family%20members%20in%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20including%20one%20that%20targeted%20his%20house%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusa%20Abu%20Marzuk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20member%20of%20Hamas's%20political%20bureau%20is%20considered%20similar%20to%20Haniyeh%20in%20his%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Marzuk%20has%20spoken%20out%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%20with%20Israel%2C%20and%20favours%20accepting%20the%20Palestinian%20borders%20drawn%20after%20the%201967%20Arab-Israeli%20war%2C%20which%20remains%20contentious%20for%20some%20within%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201990s%20he%20lived%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20raising%20funds%20for%20the%20movement's%20armed%20wing.%20He%20then%20lived%20in%20exile%2C%20including%20in%20Jordan%2C%20Egypt%20and%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20previously%20been%20mentioned%20as%20a%20possible%20successor%20to%20Hamas%20leaders%2C%20without%20success%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EZaher%20Jabarin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20long-time%20treasurer%20was%20close%20to%20Haniyeh%2C%20and%20has%20sometimes%20been%20described%20as%20one%20of%20his%20right-hand%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20detained%20in%20Israeli%20prisons%2C%20he%20was%20released%20in%202011%20as%20part%20of%20an%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Gilad%20Shalit%2C%20an%20Israeli%20soldier%20held%20hostage%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJabarin%2C%20who%20has%20strong%20ties%20with%20Turkey%2C%20where%20he%20once%20lived%2C%20has%20recruited%20people%20for%20large-scale%20money-laundering%20activities%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20were%20arrested%20in%20Israel%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20taken%20part%20in%20deadly%20operations%20carried%20out%20by%20Hamas's%20armed%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKhaled%20Meshaal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh's%20predecessor%20has%20lived%20in%20exile%20since%201967%2C%20in%20Jordan%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Syria%20and%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20propelled%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20movement%20after%20Israel%20killed%20Hamas's%20founder%2C%20Ahmed%20Yassin%2C%20and%20then%20his%20successor%20Abdelaziz%20al-Rantisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201997%20Meshaal%20survived%20a%20poisoning%20assassination%20attempt%20in%20Amman%20by%20agents%20of%20Mossad%2C%20the%20Israeli%20intelligence%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20living%20in%20Syria%2C%20he%20criticised%20the%20Damascus%20regime%20for%20its%20violent%20repression%20of%20anti-government%20protests%2C%20a%20crackdown%20which%20had%20caused%20friction%20with%20Iran%2C%20Syria's%20strategic%20ally%20and%20a%20major%20supporter%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EYahya%20Sinwar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar%2C%20elected%20in%20February%202017%20to%20lead%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20is%20a%20hardliner%20and%20an%20alleged%20mastermind%20of%20the%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ascetic%2061-year-old%20spent%2023%20years%20in%20Israeli%20prisons%20before%20being%20released%20in%202011%20as%20part%20of%20a%20prisoner%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Khan%20Yunis%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20he%20joined%20Hamas%20when%20it%20was%20founded%20in%201987%2C%20the%20year%20of%20the%20first%20intifada%20or%20uprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20go%20on%20to%20establish%20Majd%2C%20the%20group's%20internal%20security%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20elite%20commander%20in%20the%20Al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20Hamas's%20armed%20wing%2C%20is%20wanted%20by%20Israel%20and%20appears%20on%20the%20United%20States'%20list%20of%20sanctioned%20international%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar%2C%20who%20shrouds%20his%20movements%20in%20the%20highest%20secrecy%2C%20has%20not%20appeared%20in%20public%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722677520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3k7oro5g_hamas-top-leaders-_625x300_03_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-ismail-haniyeh-khaled-meshaal-to-zaher-jabarin-top-contenders-for-hamas-top-post-6254428%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palestinian%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20is%20preparing%20to%20choose%20a%20political%20leader%20after%20the%20killing%20of%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20attack%20in%20Tehran%20blamed%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-ismail-haniyeh-khaled-meshaal-to-zaher-jabarin-top-contenders-for-hamas-top-post-6254428%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-ismail-haniyeh-khaled-meshaal-to-zaher-jabarin-top-contenders-for-hamas-top-post-6254428%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-ismail-haniyeh-khaled-meshaal-to-zaher-jabarin-top-contenders-for-hamas-top-post-6254428%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Absolutely%20criminal'%3A%20Grammy%20winner%20Ricky%20Kej%20slams%20'impolite'%20Air%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722677465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.