our%20times%20to%20move%20forward%20as%20Manu's%20journey%20in%20the%20final%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20nervous%20in%20the%20final.%20I%20was%20trying%20on%20every%20shot%20but%20things%20were%20not%20working%20out.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20always%20a%20next%20time%20and%20I%20will%20try%20my%20best%20the%20next%20time%20round%2C%26quot%3B%20Manu%20said%20after%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20qualification%20on%20Friday%2C%20Bhaker%20shot%20a%20total%20of%20590%20(294%20in%20precision%2C%20296%20in%20rapid)%20out%20of%20a%20possible%20600%20to%20reach%20her%20third%20final%20of%20this%20Olympics%20at%20second%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Bhaker%20had%20won%20bronze%20in%20the%20individual%2010m%20air%20pistol%20competition%20and%20then%20combined%20with%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20to%20claim%20another%20third-place%20finish%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20event.%20Bhaker's%20second%20bronze%20had%20made%20her%20the%20first%20Indian%20after%20Independence%20to%20win%20two%20medals%20at%20the%20same%20Olympic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Manu%20Bhaker%20and%20Sarabjot%20Singh%2C%20Swapnil%20Kusale%20won%20the%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%20men's%2050m%20rifle%203P%20event.%20Kusale%20also%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20shooter%20to%20win%20a%20medal%20in%20the%20men's%2050m%20rifle%203P%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKusale%20clinched%20the%20bronze%20medal%20for%20India%20in%20the%2050m%20Rifle%203%20Positions%20Men's%20Final%20after%20finishing%20in%20third%20place%20with%20an%20aggregate%20of%20451.4.%20He%20secured%20India's%203rd%20medal%20in%20shooting%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722673200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fiipm4bb8_as_625x300_03_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fmanu-bhaker-misses-3rd-paris-olympics-2024-medal-by-just-one