n%20after%20a%20suicide%20bombing%20in%20Mogadishu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A282%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0krke24lwdo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0krke24lwdo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0krke24lwdo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Befitting%20Reputed%20Brand%26quot%3B%3A%20Grammy%20Winning%20Composer%20Blasts%20Air%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERenowned%20Indian-American%20composer%20Ricky%20Kej%2C%20a%20three-time%20Grammy%20winner%2C%20has%20publicly%20blasted%20Air%20India%20for%20downgrading%20him%20from%20business%20class%20and%20refusing%20to%20offer%20a%20refund.%20The%20musician%20claims%20this%20is%20the%20third%20time%20in%20a%20year%20that%20he%20has%20faced%20this%20issue%20with%20the%20airline%2C%20with%20no%20clarification%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kej%20shared%20his%20frustrating%20experience%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20had%20booked%20and%20paid%20for%20a%20business%20class%20ticket%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20only%20to%20be%20informed%20at%20the%20departure%20gate%20that%20he%20had%20been%20downgraded.%20The%20airline%20staff%20allegedly%20provided%20no%20reasoning%20for%20the%20downgrade%20and%20refused%20to%20give%20him%20a%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWow..%203rd%20time%20this%20is%20happening%20to%20me%20in%20one%20year.%20I%20booked%20and%20paid%20for%20a%20business%20class%20ticket%20on%20air%20india%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Bengaluru.%20When%20I%20reach%20departure%20gate%2C%20the%20staff%20rudely%20tells%20me%20that%20I%20have%20been%20downgraded%20(for%20no%20reason)%20and%20they%20cannot%20give%20me%20a%20refund.%20What's%20up%20with%20Air%20India%3F%26quot%3B%20Kej%20wrote%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAir%20India%20really%20needs%20to%20introspect%20and%20see%20if%20they%20are%20capable%20of%20running%20an%20airline%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20I%20am%20currently%20at%20the%20departure%20gate.%20Flight%20taking%20off%20at%209.25am%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESince%20this%20%26quot%3Bdowngrading%26quot%3B%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fairindia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40airindia%3C%2Fa%3E%20happens%20so%20often%20(3%20times%20just%20with%20me)%2C%20you%20would%20imagine%20that%20they%20have%20protocol%20in%20place.%20Immediate%20refund%2C%20options%20for%20other%20flights%2C%20immediate%20intimation%20and%20apology%20for%20discomfort.%20They%20do%20none%20of%20the%20above%2C%20and%20instead%20are%20rude%2C%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ricky%20Kej%20(%40rickykej)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frickykej%2Fstatus%2F1819581680392228878%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20criticised%20the%20airline's%20response%2C%20stating%20that%20they%20had%20no%20protocol%20in%20place%20for%20such%20situations%20and%20instead%20were%20%26quot%3Brude%2C%20clueless%2C%20high-handed%2C%20and%20behaved%20as%20if%20they%20were%20doing%20a%20huge%20favor%26quot%3B%20by%20allowing%20him%20to%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20ok%20to%20have%20operational%20issues%20due%20to%20unforseen%20circumstances.%20But%20to%20not%20provide%20quick%20and%20effective%20resolutions%20for%20the%20same%20is%20absolutely%20criminal..%20and%20not%20befitting%20of%20a%20reputed%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20responded%20to%20Mr%20Kej's%20thread%2C%20asking%20to%20resolve%20the%20matter%20privately%2C%20but%20their%20move%20backfired%20when%20the%20composer%20demanded%20a%20clear%20refund%20amount%20and%20explanation.%20After%20receiving%20a%20service%20call%20from