Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20requested%20the%20deployment%20of%20advanced%20radar%20equipment%2C%20including%20one%20Xaver%20radar%20and%20four%20Reeco%20radars%2C%20which%20will%20be%20airlifted%20from%20Delhi%20in%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20aircraft%2C%20along%20with%20their%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20said%20that%20the%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations%20have%20entered%20their%20final%20stages%2C%20but%20206%20people%20are%20still%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20here%2C%20he%20said%20there%20is%20difficulty%20in%20identifying%20the%20dead%20bodies%20and%20parts%20recovered%20from%20the%20Chaliyar%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20now%2C%20215%20bodies%20have%20been%20recovered%2C%20of%20which%2087%20are%20women%2C%2098%20are%20men%2C%20and%2030%20are%20children.%20As%20many%20as%20148%20bodies%20have%20been%20handed%20over%20so%20far.%20There%20are%20206%20people%20missing.%20Eighty-one%20people%20are%20injured%20and%20are%20under%20treatment%20in%20various%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20rehabilitation%20efforts%2C%20Vijayan%20said%20a%20secure%20region%20will%20be%20identified%20and%20a%20township%20will%20be%20constructed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20education%20minister%20will%20visit%20the%20schools%20destroyed%20in%20the%20region%2C%20and%20the%20education%20department%20will%20take%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20studies%20of%20the%20disaster-struck%20children%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20also%20saw%20the%20arrival%20of%20Malayalam%20superstar%20Mohanlal%20in%20the%20landslides%20ravaged%20areas%20of%20Mundakkai%20and%20Chooralmala%2C%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20an%20honorary%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20in%20the%20Territorial%20Army%2C%20to%20oversee%20the%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonning%20army%20fatigues%2C%20the%20actor%20held%20a%20brief%20discussion%20with%20officers%20at%20the%20Army%20camp%20in%20Meppadi%20before%20visiting%20Chooralmala%2C%20Mundakkai%20and%20Punchirimattom%2C%20among%20other%20places%2C%20and%20interacting%20with%20the%20various%20rescue%20workers%2C%20including%20the%20Army%20and%20the%20locals%2C%20to%20get%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20landslides-hit%20areas%2C%20Mohanlal%2C%20who%20was%20conferred%20the%20Lt%20Colonel%20post%20in%20the%20territorial%20army%20in%202009%2C%20was%20briefed%20about%20the%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations%20by%20the%20army%20officers%20and%20thereafter%2C%20he%20interacted%20with%20mediapersons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20interaction%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20natural%20disasters%20ever%20seen%20in%20the%20country%20and%20thanked%20everyone%20involved%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Viswasanthi%20Foundation%2C%20founded%20by%20him%2C%20has%20pledged%20Rs%20three%20crore%20for%20the%20rehabilitation%20works%20in%20the%20disaster-hit%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor-cum-director%20and%20retired%20army%20officer%20Major%20Ravi%2C%20who%20accompanied%20Mohanlal%2C%20said%20that%20as%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20foundation%2C%20he%20was%20promising%20that%20they%20would%20rebuild%20the%20Mundakkai%20LP%20school%2C%20which%20stands%20in%20ruins%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20making%20donations%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Disaster%20Relief%20Fund%20(CMDRF)%20created%20a%20ripple%20within%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20announcement%20by%20senior%20party%20leader%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%20that%20he%20would%20donate%20to%20it%20one%20month's%20salary%2C%20which%20he%20draws%20as%20an%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20drew%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20his%20party%20colleague%20and%20KPCC%20chief%2C%20K%20Sudhakaran%2C%20who%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20expressed%20displeasure%20by%20saying%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20give%20money%20to%20the%20funds%20managed%20by%20the%20CPI(M)-led%20Left%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20directive%20(from%20the%20Kerala%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee)%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20government's%20fund%20(CMDRF)%2C%26quot%3B%20Sudhakaran%20told%20a%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Congress%20was%20raising%20funds%20to%20help%20the%20affected%20people%2C%20and%20Chennithala%20should%20have%20contributed%20to%20that%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudhakaran's%20statement%20comes%20amidst%20online%20smear%20campaigns%20discouraging%20people%20from%20sending%20funds%20to%20the%20CMDRF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20lodged%2039%20FIRs%20till%20Friday%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20smear%20campaigns%20against%20the%20CM's%20Facebook%20post%20requesting%20help%20for%20the%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20also%20said%20that%2C%20as%20of%20Friday%2C%20279%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20found%20campaigning%20against%20donations%20to%20the%20CMDRF%20and%20that%20notices%20had%20been%20issued%20to%20remove%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20the%20smear%20campaigns%2C%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20--%20be%20it%20an%20elderly%20tea%20stall%20owner%20or%20children%20--%20have%20been%20reportedly%20donating%20their%20meagre%20earnings%20or%20pocket%20money%20of%20varying%20amounts%20to%20the%20fund.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722672360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht