C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20girls%20door-to-door%20to%20motivate%20people%20and%20explain%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20consuming%20liquor%2C%20regular%20consumption%20of%20necessary%20drugs%2C%20and%20more.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20girls%20door-to-door%20to%20motivate%20people%20about%20regular%20consumption%20of%20necessary%20drugs%20and%20explain%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20consuming%20liquor.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20has%20not%20been%20easier%20for%20the%20administration.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20idea%20of%20empowerment%20is%20least%20understood%20in%20villages.%20They%20question%20why%20they%20should%20invest%20in%20this%20project%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20an%20asset%20building%20program%20in%20the%20tangible%20sense%2C%20nobody%20is%20building%20a%20road%2C%20nobody%20is%20getting%20somebody%20to%20inaugurate%20it.%20There%20is%20no%20funding%20attached%20to%20the%20project.%20So%2C%20people%20naturally%20take%20less%20interest%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Minal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20identify%20people%20who%20are%20motivated%20at%20the%20human%20resource%20front%2C%20who%20understand%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20build%20a%20human%20resource%20and%20thereby%20future