r%20as%20we%20had%20complementary%20skill%20sets.%20We%20would%20teach%20each%20other%20the%20subjects%20we%20were%20strong%20in.%20Sachin%20also%20served%20as%20a%20benchmark%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nandini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Study%20buddies%20Nandini%20and%20Sachin%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358909%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudy%20buddies%20Nandini%20and%20Sachin%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20on%20the%20feedback%2C%20they%20were%20better%20prepared.%20While%20the%20exams%20are%20usually%20held%20in%20May%20each%20year%2C%20in%202021%2C%20owing%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20were%20postponed%20to%20July.%20Those%20two%20extra%20months%20served%20as%20a%20major%20boon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20their%20guard%20down%20even%20with%20the%20extra%20time%E2%80%94they%20had%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize.%20They%20did%20another%20revision%20and%20solved%20past%20papers%2C%20revision%20test%20papers%2C%20and%20mock%20test%20papers.%20For%20subjects%20they%20found%20difficult%2C%20like%20SFM%2C%20they%20spent%20extra%20time%2C%20which%20proved%20useful%20as%20they%20scored%20very%20well%20in%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348078%2Fdelhi-constable-than-singh-ki-pathshala-teaches-underprivileged-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocused%20and%20studied%20hard%20%3C%2Fa%3Eright%20from%20the%20start%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20stress%20too%20much%20before%20the%20exam.%20Spend%20more%20time%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20your%20study%20holidays.%20This%20will%20increase%20your%20confidence%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nandini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreparation%20tips%20from%20the%20CA%20rankers%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStart%20full-blown%20preparation%20six%20to%20seven%20months%20before%20the%20exam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFinish%20your%20lectures%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20focus%20on%20self-study.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudy%20from%20the%20ICAI%20modules%2C%20past%20question%20papers%2C%20and%20revision%20test%20papers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMake%20a%20proper%20plan%20and%20stick%20to%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBe%20consistent%20and%20focused.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nandini%20Agrawal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722260168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358900%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sachin%20and%20Nandini%20Agrawal%20had%20a%20single%20goal%20since%20childhood%20--%20to%20become%20chartered%20accountants.%20Two%20years%20apart%20in%20age%2C%20the%20siblings%20cleared%20CA%20exams%20together%2C%20with%20Nandini%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20CA%20in%20the%20world.%20Here's%20how%20they%20prepared.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358900%2Fchartered-accountant-siblings-cracked-ca-together-final-exam-tips-lessons-study-plan-articleship-madhya-pradesh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Natural%20Farming%2C%20Solar%20Energy%20%26amp%3B%20More%3A%20Will%20Budget%202024%20Push%20India%20to%20a%20Greener%20Future%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20focus%20was%20on%20employment%2C%20skills%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Micro%2C%20Small%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20(MSMEs)%20and%20farmers%2C%20there%20were%20some%20interesting%20new%20ideas%20presented%20in%20the%20latest%20Budget%20by%20Finance%20Secretary%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20on%2023%20July%20to%20make%20India%20greener.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20agriculture%2C%20the%20government%20strengthened%20its%20support%20for%20natural%20farming.%20Originally%20spear-headed%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%2C%20natural%20farming%20(then%20known%20as%20zero-budget%20natural%20farming)%20was%20first%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20Budget%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20reiterated%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20initiate%20one%20crore%20farmers%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F220301%2Fpunjab-farmer-organic-vegetables-family-health-wife-safe-natural-food-india-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20farming%20techniques%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20plans%20to%20open%2010%2C000%20bio-input%20resource%20centres%2C%20and%20has%20promised%20resources%20to%20help%20customers%20locate%20and%20differentiate%20natural%20produce%20from%20chemical-based%20agriculture%20by%20providing%20improved%20branding%20and%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrop%20breeding%20research%20will%20be%20focussed%20on%20again%20in%20response%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20climate%20change.%20The%20government%20plans%20to%20release%20109%20climate-adapted%2C%20high-yielding%20varieties%20of%2032%20horticulture%20and%20cereal%20crops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESalient%20features%20of%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F256076%2Fhow-to-single-use-plastic-ban-rules-states-india-waste-management-reduce-reuse-sustainable-civis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechniques%20used%20in%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20based%20on%20the%20scientific%20and%20ecological%20insights%20of%20our%20ancestors%2C%20stress%20on%20the%20creation%20of%20healthy%20carbon-rich%20soil%20ecosystems%20using%20bio-inputs%20to%20stimulate%20fungi%20and%20microbes%2C%20along%20with%20cropping%20systems%20integrating%20trees%2C%20crops%2C%20herbs%20and%20livestock.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20great%20diversity%20of%20crops%20within%20a%20field%20provides%20the%20farmer%20resilience%20against%20the%20failure%20of%20one%20crop%20as%20well%20as%20providing%20habitat%20for%20natural%20predators%20that%20control%20pests.%20The%20tenets%20of%20natural%20farming%20%E2%80%94%20applying%20cow%20manure%20and%20urine%20to%20the%20seeds%20and%20soil%2C%20maintaining%20year-round%20soil-cover%2C%20banning%20crop%20burning%2C%20replacing%20monocultures%20with%20a%20mosaic%20of%20trees%2C%20shrubs%2C%20and%20herbs%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20is%20now%20common%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farms%20which%20have%20adopted%20this%20technique%20have%20slashed%20input%20costs%20along%20with%20the%20use%20of%20irrigation%20water%2C%20while%20maintaining%20incomes%20and%20producing%20healthier%20food%20that%20commands%20premium%20prices%20in%20the%20markets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20transport%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20themes%20of%20the%20Budget%20was%20to%20plough%20improved%20public%20finances%20into%20increased%20infrastructure%20spending.%20Apart%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350255%2Fchhavi-rajawat-sarpanch-mba-soda-village-rajasthan-water-roads-college-digital-literacy-help-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20on%20roads%20and%20railways%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20an%20intriguing%20announcement%20to%20fund%20the%20development%20of%20Transport%20Oriented%20Development%20(TOD)%20plans%20for%2014%20large%20cities%20with%20more%20than%203%20million%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20still%20at%20an%20early%20stage%2C%20if%20the%20TOD%20plan%20succeeds%2C%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20transform%20urban%20living.%20Though%20still%20novel%20in%20India%2C%20TOD%20is%20common%20in%20many%20east%20Asian%20countries.%20Such%20developments%20create%20highly%20liveable%2C%20compact%20neighbourhoods%20where%20public%20transport%20and%20walking%20are%20favoured%20over%20motor%20cars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20concept%20is%20for%20planners%20to%20grant%20new%20developments%20around%20metro%20stations%20with%20high%20Floor-to-Area-Ratios%2C%20restrict%20residential%20parking%20spaces%20and%20improve%20pedestrian%20facilities%20using%20tunnels%2C%20bridges%20and%20covered%20footpaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong%20has%20used%20TOD%20since%20the%201970s.%20The%20development%20board%20acquired%20land%20through%20compulsory%20purchase%20at%20the%20prevailing%20price%20before%20the%20new%20transport%20route%20was%20announced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20submit%20bids%20to%20acquire%20the%20rights%20to%20develop%20mixed%20use%20commercial%20and%20residential%20buildings%20around%20the%20new%20metro%20stations.%20This%20policy%20was%20instrumental%20in%20creating%20the%20skyscrapers%20that%20form%20the%20iconic%20Hong%20Kong%20skyline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revenue%20earned%20by%20the%20city%20from%20this%20%E2%80%98land%20value%20capture%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20enough%20to%20fully%20fund%20the%20construction%20of%20new%20metro%20lines.%20By%20way%20of%20contrast%2C%20most%20cities%20with%20a%20metro%20rely%20on%20huge%20capital%20grants%20from%20the%20municipality%20or%20national%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20urban%20development%20ministry%20publishes%20workable%20plans%20to%20retrofit%20TOD%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20haphazard%20city%20zoning%20and%20on-going%20plans%20to%20build%20metros%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20In%20China%2C%20the%20government%20seems%20less%20inhibited%20about%20compulsorily%20acquiring%20land%20and%20funnelling%20the%20profits%20from%20rezoning%20into%20public%20goods.%20The%20tradition%20in%20India%20isn%E2%80%99t%20so%20communitarian.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEnergy%20policy%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20does%20not%20say%20much%20about%20energy%20policy%20and%20expenditure%20signalling%20continuity%20with%20its%20pre-election%20policy.%20Back%20in%202022%2C%20India%20updated%20its%20%E2%80%9Cnationally-determined%20contributions%E2%80%9D%20(international%20commitments%20under%20the%20Paris%20climate%20agreement)%20and%20has%20a%20set%20of%20energy%20policies%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProgress%20is%20being%20made%20increasing%20generation%20capacity%20to%2050%25%20which%20is%20projected%20to%20be%20met%20by%20zero-carbon%20electricity%20by%202030.%20In%20support%20of%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20objective%2C%20customs%20duty%20is%20being%20abolished%20for%20goods%20involved%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309007%2Fprof-ravindra-gettu-iit-madras-scientists-recycle-waste-concrete-using-solar-thermal-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20manufacture%20of%20solar%20cells%20and%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20stimulate%20assembling%20of%20such%20parts%20locally%20and%20will%20also%20marginally%20reduce%20the%20price%20of%20solar%20PV%20installations.%20The%20funding%20for%20the%20PM-Surya%20Ghar%20scheme%20supporting%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20crore%20solar%20PV%20homes%20was%20held%20at%20Rs%2075%2C021%20crore.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20announced%20funding%20for%20a%20new%20800%20MW%20thermal%20power%20plant%20operated%20as%20a%20NTPC-BHEL%20joint%20venture%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20push%20for%20sustainable%20initiatives%2C%20this%20funding%20will%20use%20ultra-super%20critical%20coal%20technology%2C%20which%20despite%20being%20less%20carbon%20intensive%20than%20the%20older%20technology%2C%20will%20remain%20a%20major%20source%20of%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGreen%20taxonomy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20energy%20transition%20needs%20huge%20and%20sustained%20investment%20in%20green%20infrastructure.%20The%20sums%20are%20so%20large%20and%20the%20threats%20so%20near%20that%20international%20climate%20finance%20needs%20to%20supplement%20local%20funding%20sources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20announced%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20produce%20a%20taxonomy%20for%20climate%20finance%20to%20classify%20legitimate%20green%20projects%20and%20call-out%20the%20greenwash.%20The%20EU%20commission%20and%20the%20Chinese%20financial%20regulators%20pioneered%20the%20publication%20of%20green%20taxonomies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20creation%20of%20a%20taxonomy%20will%20take%20time%2C%20and%20there%20might%20be%20merit%20in%20India%20simply%20copying%20either%20the%20EU%E2%80%99s%20or%20the%20Chinese%20model%20with%20minimal%20changes.%20Their%20development%20involves%20technical%20experts%20systematically%20looking%20at%20different%20economic%20branches%2C%20like%20agriculture%20or%20electricity%20generation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20specify%20which%20activities%20qualify%20as%20%E2%80%98green%E2%80%99%20investments%20that%20make%20a%20meaningful%20contribution%20to%20our%20environmental%20challenges%2C%20and%20which%20do%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20EU%20taxonomy%20wind%20and%20solar%20power%20generation%2C%20the%20manufacture%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F283038%2Fbengaluru-startup-micelio-mobility-invests-crores-india-ev-infrastructure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurchase%20of%20EV%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%20qualify%20while%20the%20use%20of%20gas%20or%20coal%20%E2%80%94%20even%20ultra-super%20critical%20coal%20and%20hybrid%20transport%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20do%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%E2%80%99s%20taxonomy%20is%20aligned%20to%20the%20international%20norms%2C%20it%20should%20help%20international%20green%20investors%20quickly%20sift%20through%20projects%2C%20funds%20and%20debt%20instruments%20certified%20with%20the%20Indian%20taxonomy%20that%20meet%20their%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202017%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298273%2Fsebi-consultation-paper-green-debt-securities-invest-in-sustainable-finance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20published%20and%20updated%20green%20debt%20guidelines%20that%20ensure%20promoters%20of%20green%20financial%20products%2C%20explaining%20exactly%20how%20investors%E2%80%99%20money%20would%20be%20spent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20guidelines%20provided%20transparency%2C%20they%20gave%20a%20lot%20of%20wiggle%20room%20for%20%E2%80%98mildly%E2%80%99%20green%20projects%20to%20be%20funded%20even%20if%20they%20are%20not%20green%20enough%20to%20contribute%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20or%20biodiversity%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taxonomy%20will%20hopefully%20set%20tough%20green%20standards%20that%20ensure%20the%20investment%20progresses%20India%E2%80%99s%20Nationally%20Determined%20Contribution%20(NDC).%20When%20the%20taxonomy%20is%20published%2C%20we%20should%20check%20to%20ensure%20that%20fossil%20fuel%20generation%20and%20non-organic%20agriculture%20are%20excluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taxonomy%20could%20also%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(RBI)%20green%20bank%20deposits%2C%20thus%20ensuring%20savers%20funds%20only%20lent%20for%20genuinely%20green%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20first%20budget%20for%20the%20current%20coalition%20government%20has%20made%20incremental%20progress%20on%20old%20themes%20like%20solar%20power%20generation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F196917%2Fgujarat-farmer-zero-budget-natural-farming-double-income-organic-vegetables-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20opens%20up%20planning%20and%20discussion%20of%20game-changing%20new%20ideas%20in%20urban%20development%2Fpublic%20transport%20and%20green%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Prashant%20Vaze%20who%20is%20a%20Goa-based%20writer%20and%20environmental%20economist.%20He%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20career%20in%20the%20UK%20civil%20service%2C%20but%20now%20focuses%20on%20climate%20finance%20issues.%20He%20has%20published%20a%20number%20of%20climate%20fiction%20short-stories%20and%20technical%20articles%20on%20climate%2C%20the%20energy%20transition%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EUnion%20Budget%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocuments%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202024-25.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EZero%20budget%20natural%20farming%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvikaspedia.in%2Fagriculture%2Fbest-practices%2Fsustainable-agriculture%2Fclimate-smart-agriculture%2Fzero-budget-natural-farming-in-andhra-pradesh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVikaspedia.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arup.com%2Finsights%2Fis-transit-oriented-development-tod-the-solution%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520TOD%2520at%2520Kowloon%2520station%2C%252C%2520rail%2520connections%252C%2520and%2520taxis.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Is%20Transit%20Oriented%20Development%20(TOD)%20the%20solution%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EPublished%20by%20Gaurav%20Ahuja%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3Eon%20Arup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ein%20March%202020.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sebi.gov.in%2Flegal%2Fcirculars%2Fmay-2017%2Fdisclosure-requirements-for-issuance-and-listing-of-green-debt-securities_34988.html%5C%22%3EDisclosure%20Requirements%20for%20Issuance%20and%20Listing%20of%20Green%20Debt%20Securities%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20SEBI%20in%20March%202017.%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722254409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358913%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20proposing%20a%20slew%20of%20measures%20to%20reduce%20India's%20carbon%20emission%20in%20Budget%202024%2C%20here%20are%20some%20propositions%20likely%20to%20help%20the%20agriculture%20and%20transport%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358913%2Fbudget-2024-green-measures-natural-farming-solar-energy-taxonomy-electric-vehicle%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Started%20With%20Few%20Jars%20on%20The%20Roadside%2C%20How%20a%20Homemaker%20Built%20Her%20Pickle%20Empire%20Earning%20Rs%205%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Krishna%20Yadav%20stood%20before%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20holding%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20for%20Diversified%20Agriculture.%20Her%20entire%20life%20journey%20flashed%20before%20her%20eyes%20as%20she%20gazed%20at%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20the%20small%20village%20of%20Daulatpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Krishna%20never%20attended%20school.%20After%20her%20marriage%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Bulandshahr%2C%20where%20she%20faced%20a%20dire%20situation%20when%20her%20husband%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20traffic%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLater%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20start%20a%20vehicle%20trading%20business%2C%20but%20we%20incurred%20huge%20losses.%20We%20had%20to%20sell%20our%20two%20houses%2C%20each%20spread%20across%20150%20%3Cem%3Egaj%20%3C%2Fem%3E(approximately%201%2C300%20sqft).%20It%20became%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20survive.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20eat%20vegetables%20anymore%20and%20survived%20on%20%3Cem%3Enamak%20roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(salt%20and%20flatbread)%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20With%20only%20Rs%20500%20in%20her%20pocket%2C%20she%20relocated%20to%20the%20city%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20three%20young%20children.%20%E2%80%9CI%20looked%20for%20jobs%2C%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20education%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20work.%20My%20husband%20also%20struggled%20to%20find%20employment.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20we%20began%20working%20on%20a%20field%20through%20sharecropping%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharecropping%20is%20a%20legal%20arrangement%20where%20a%20landowner%20permits%20a%20tenant%20to%20cultivate%20their%20land%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20crops%20produced.%20The%20five-member%20family%20began%20living%20in%20a%20small%20room%20on%20the%20field.%20They%20spent%20their%20days%20cultivating%20vegetables%2C%20but%20the%20income%20from%20their%20efforts%20was%20insufficient%20to%20sustain%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20price%20of%20vegetables%20in%20the%20market%20would%20fluctuate%20and%20we%20would%20hardly%20earn%20any%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starting%20with%20karonda%20(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358852%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20Krishna%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20life%20when%20she%20heard%20about%20a%20training%20programme%20on%20value%20addition%20of%20post-harvest%20losses%20through%20a%20television%20programme.%20She%20enrolled%20in%20a%20course%20at%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20where%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAmit%2520tells%2520The%2520Better%2520India%2Ctastes%2520it%2520becomes%2520a%2520fan.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emastered%20the%20art%20and%20science%20of%20making%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurabba%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marmalade).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20path%20for%20her%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Rs%20500%20to%20Rs%205%20crore%20empire%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20an%20enthused%20student%2C%20Krishna%20would%20set%20out%20to%20the%20training%20centre%20with%20post-harvest%20losses%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%20from%20her%20field%2C%20a%20few%20spices%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20utensils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20grew%20up%20seeing%20my%20%3Cem%3Edadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Enani%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmothers)%20make%20pickles%2C%20the%20know-how%20that%20I%20learnt%20in%20the%20training%20was%20insightful.%20As%20homemakers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20calculate%20the%20amounts%20of%20spices%20and%20salt%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20pickle.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20ways%20to%20enhance%20the%20taste%20as%20well%20as%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20pickles%20naturally.%20The%20key%20was%20the%20measurement%20of%20spices%20and%20oils%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Krishna%20started%20making%20the%20pickles%2C%20but%20she%20had%20little%20knowledge%20of%20commercialising%20the%20products.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20set%20up%20a%20small%20table%20on%20the%20roadside%20and%20put%20our%20products%20on%20display.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20very%20busy%20road%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20attract%20people%20to%20our%20stall.%20So%2C%20we%20placed%20two%20large%20earthen%20pots%20of%20water%20along%20with%20the%20pickles.%20I%20offered%20pickles%20as%20samples%20to%20those%20who%20stopped%20to%20drink%20free%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20simple%20yet%20effective%20strategy%20slowly%20built%20her%20customer%20base.%20She%20also%20started%20participating%20in%20local%20fairs%20to%20promote%20the%20products.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20her%20pickles%20grew%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20formally%20launch%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20eventually%20open%20her%20own%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20Today%2C%20she%20offers%20over%20250%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300822%2Fsenior-citizen-entrepreneur-sheila-pickles-jams-traditional-kerala-recipes-home-business-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarieties%20of%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20herbal%20juices%2C%20chutneys%2C%20marmalades%2C%20and%20syrups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358853%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKrishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Rohilla%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20for%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20pickles%20perfectly%20capture%20the%20essence%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomemade%20goodness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20offering%20a%20nostalgic%20taste.%20Their%20wide%20variety%20of%20flavours%20caters%20to%20every%20palate%20and%20mood.%20Whenever%20I%20open%20one%20of%20their%20jars%2C%20it%20bursts%20with%20authentic%20tastes%20and%20aromas%2C%20enhancing%20my%20simple%20meals.%20These%20pickles%20never%20disappoint%2C%20consistently%20maintaining%20their%20taste%20and%20quality%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20has%20established%20a%20five-storey%20facility%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20manufactures%2010%20to%2020%20quintals%20of%20pickles%20daily%2C%20and%20her%20company%20boasts%20an%20impressive%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20extraordinary%20determination%20and%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%2C%20she%20has%20been%20recognised%20with%20multiple%20awards%20including%20the%20Outstanding%20Women%20Award%20from%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%202012%3B%20the%20Innovative%20Award%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20allied%20activities%20during%20the%20Global%20Agriculture%20Summit%202013%3B%20and%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Award%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20homemaker%20and%20my%20core%20job%20was%20to%20look%20after%20the%20household%20duties.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20family%20income%20in%20our%20dire%20times.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20let%20my%20children%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20our%20financial%20crisis.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20and%20I%20never%20imagined%20I%20would%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20eldest%20son%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20business%2C%20while%20her%20other%20two%20children%20are%20currently%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20have%20both%20%3Cem%3Egaadi%20bangla%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20car%20and%20a%20bungalow)%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20dignity%20to%20walk%20with%20pride.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20on%20television%2C%20and%20that%20dream%20came%20true%20with%20my%20business.%20However%2C%20achieving%20this%20success%20required%20consistent%20hard%20work.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20stop%20now%2C%20I%20would%20risk%20losing%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20example%2C%20Krishna%20emphasises%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20adversity%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20resilience.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20be%20bogged%20down%20by%20failures.%20Do%20not%20view%20helplessness%20or%20failure%20as%20a%20setback%20but%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20greater%20achievements.%20If%20one%20door%20closes%2C%20many%20others%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722240366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Krishna%20Yadav%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20began%20selling%20pickles%20on%20the%20roadside.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20established%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20growing%20her%20business%20into%20a%20successful%20enterprise%20with%20over%20250%20varieties%20of%20products%20and%20a%20five-storey%20factory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358846%2Futtar-pradesh-krishna-yadav-pickle-business-delhi-earn-crores-woman-empowerment%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Southwest%20Airlines%20Shakes%20Up%20Its%20Seating%20Rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Southwest%20Airlines%20will%20also%20offer%20redeye%20flights%20for%20the%20first%20time.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721905992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F66a2323a2400008f135480a1.jpeg%3Fcache%3DpzSvOdxBTd%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fairlines-results_n_66a23238e4b0ac6125bd8d5b%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Southwest%20Airlines%20will%20als